{"tid":1003453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普: 中國必須開放金融業、製造業、農業、工商業 市場","createTime":"2019-01-31T16:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T09:49:59.000Z","uid":62257,"like":160,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"64aeb71442677a975ebe354b4593c80abd21d4ba","tid":1003453,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2052021/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2052021%2F&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=3971aaf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2052021/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/01/31/2052021_bcd0b673ec79bdd061ecb39f9d6ee2cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F01%2F31%2F2052021_bcd0b673ec79bdd061ecb39f9d6ee2cd.png&h=d22be136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普再次在社交媒體發文，談及正在進行的新一輪中美貿易談判。他表示，中國必須向美國開放包括金融在內的市場，否則雙方難以達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在帖文稱，期待中國不但開放其推進中的金融服務業，其他行業包括製造業、農業，以及涉及美國的工商業，也能同時向美國開放，否則，本輪中美貿易會談仍難以達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n中美高級別官員周三開始一連兩日展開新一輪貿易談判，中國國務院副總理劉鶴預定周四稍後與特朗普會面，為本次會談畫下注腳。"},{"pid":"e4fec2da5c26ab0a7ac54de1bf83a2bdcd73e005","tid":1003453,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5f508a35bfca7d448e4619d744aec98d3b9359","tid":1003453,"uid":121146,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次講完my friend就撚獲勁既"},{"pid":"6e1f74ad9c90903e506a8d8374739b0057f45e0f","tid":1003453,"uid":41257,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"同中國講自由 即係繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"h